author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be 4chan returning back online after it was hacked and leaked for the world to see. The way this site was hacked is actually quite embarrassing and it should have you a bit on edge if you use similar websites. How was it so easy to hack the largest imageboard? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: 4Chan Just Came Back Online...
